msgid "The Nameserver Addresses are typically specified via <emphasis role=\"italics\">nameserver</emphasis> directives in the file <emphasis role=\"bold\">/etc/resolv.conf</emphasis>. For more information, view the system manual page for resolv.conf with the command:"
